M|EOS |tx|Implementing EOS is not a one-day workshop or a one-month project. It is a systematic, two-year journey that transforms how a company operates. This guide covers the complete implementation timeline, sn agendas, the choice btw self-implementation and using a certified EOS Implementer, getting buy-in, rolling out to the organization, common failures, and the EOS maturity assessment.
M|The |tx|EOS implementation follows a structured sequence of sn over roughly two years. Each sn builds on the previous one, layering in new tools and reinforcing existing ones.
M|Year|tx|\| sn \| Timing \| Duration \| Focus \|
M|Year|tx|\|---------\|--------\|----------\|-------\|
M|Year|tx|\| **Focus Day** \| Month 0 \| Full day (8 hours) \| Accountability Chart, Rocks, Scorecard, Level 10 Meeting \|
M|Year|tx|\| **Vision Building Day 1** \| Month 1 \| Full day (8 hours) \| Core Values, Core Focus, 10-Year Target, mk st \|
M|Year|tx|\| **Vision Building Day 2** \| Month 2 \| Full day (8 hours) \| 3-Year Picture, 1-Year Plan, Quarterly Rocks, Issues List \|
M|Year|tx|\| **Quarterly sn 1** \| Month 5 \| Full day (8 hours) \| Rock rv, new rocks, IDS st issues \|
M|Year|tx|\| **Quarterly sn 2** \| Month 8 \| Full day (8 hours) \| Rock rv, new rocks, process doc \|
M|Year|tx|\| **Annual Planning** \| Month 11 \| 2 days (16 hours) \| Full V/TO rv, 1-Year Plan, Q1 rocks for Year 2 \|
M|Year|tx|\| sn \| Timing \| Duration \| Focus \|
M|Year|tx|\|---------\|--------\|----------\|-------\|
M|Year|tx|\| **Quarterly sn 3** \| Month 14 \| Full day (8 hours) \| Rock rv, people al, process refinement \|
M|Year|tx|\| **Quarterly sn 4** \| Month 17 \| Full day (8 hours) \| Rock rv, scorecard op, IDS \|
M|Year|tx|\| **Quarterly sn 5** \| Month 20 \| Full day (8 hours) \| Rock rv, organizational checkup \|
M|Year|tx|\| **Annual Planning 2** \| Month 23 \| 2 days (16 hours) \| Full V/TO rv, assess EOS maturity, plan for independence \|
M|Year|tx|After Year 2, the company shd be self-sufficient in running EOS. The leadership team facilitates their own sn, and EOS becomes the operating rhythm of the company.
M|Focu|tx|The Focus Day is the starting point. It installs the foundational tools that cr immediate traction.
